# supportsSecureCoding

**Type Property**

A Boolean value indicating whether the [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSURLRequest] implements the [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSSecureCoding] protocol.

## Declaration

```swift
class var supportsSecureCoding: Bool { get }
```

## Return Value

[doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/true] to indicate that `NSURLRequest` implements the [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSSecureCoding] protocol.
